  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5673763/" class="title-link">品味一代大师的功力</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5673763"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u36771726-14.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36771726/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">唐山</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-11-28"
      class="main-meta">2012-11-28 22:09:56</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5673763_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这两本书，是明史大家顾诚先生的论文合集。  说顾诚先生是大师，有三个原因。  首先是他扎实的治学精神，传承了朴学的传统，以《李岩质疑》为例，在引用县志记载时，能遍览著书，从不同版本中比较出前后改易之处，短短的一篇文章，容纳了惊人的阅读量。  其次是能发人所未发，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5673763/#comments">(39回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5673763_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5673763_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





